  m_text: "Welcome to your Storage! Here you can manage your Mons and even fuse them
    together.\n\nHere's how fusion works: \n\n\t1. Press the Fusion button and select
    two Mons.\n\n\t2. One Mon will become the Body, keeping its \n\tappearance and
    base stats.\n\n\t3. The newly fused Mon will inherit a random \n\tability from
    the second one!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41c247ff97b5bba40a0a17299131cfd8, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 7969565418680184718, guid: 41c247ff97b5bba40a0a17299131cfd8, type: 2}
